summary: Two presets from the lost piece of the reclusive cannibal cult family.
descriptionHtml:
[center][size=3]Two Nord Presets of my Characters whose time has drawn to a close. 
So instead of letting them fade away, I've decided to share them with you! 
[/size]
Ferran Volkihar 
He was the main character of my longest running story. 
Cold, cunning, and ever hunted by the Vigilant and Dawnguard for sins of the past...

Zyphr Volkihar
Son of Ferran. Foolhardy, arrogant, and always ready for a fight. 
Enjoys hunting dragons, mainly after his parents were burnt to a crisp by Alduin.
